article.headline: Bello's 19 lead Purdue Fort Wayne past Southeast Missouri State 89-80
article.description: — Rasheed Bello scored 19 points as Purdue Fort Wayne beat Southeast Missouri State 89-80 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Bello's 19 lead Purdue Fort Wayne past Southeast Missouri State 89-80
article.story: FORT WAYNE, Ind. -- — Rasheed Bello scored 19 points as Purdue Fort Wayne beat Southeast Missouri State 89-80 on Saturday night. Bello added five assists for the Mastodons (10-1). Anthony Roberts added 15 points, six rebounds and three steals. Quinton Morton-Robertson had 15 points. TJ Biel led the way for the Redhawks (3-7) with 23 points and nine rebounds. Rob Martin added 22 points and five assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
